cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a novel deep reinforcement learning architecture that integrates both model-free and model-based learning. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). The focus on MuJoCo environments also suggests a potential fit with the robotics and control sub-categories.
